  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Ville Montefiori is made up of four Italian villas. It's in the most peaceful location on a hill above the lake, and the gardens are perfectly landscaped with sculptures dotted around them. It feels like you've come to a little hideaway. It's decorated in an ornate Italian style with lots of gold gilding, chandeliers and rich colours.</p>
<p>The hotel has great spa facilities with a sauna, steam room and whirlpool, as well as two swimming pools, which are the place to be when you're not out discovering <a data-udi="umb://document/7c2039e31003455f9c5af8c11e6f0e11" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7c2039e31003455f9c5af8c11e6f0e11}" title="Gardone Riviera">Gardone</a>. We'd recommend walking along to Gardone Sopra and checking out the Vittoriale Museum and gardens. You're only a 12 minute walk away from this historic town and all the restaurants, cafes and bars it has to offer. In the evening come back and have a drink on the terrace, it has a fantastic panoramic view of the lake. </p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 1 hour 30 mins by coach.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
