  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms </strong>are about 20m² and sleep up to two people. They have a balcony, shower, hairdryer, air conditioning, safe, TV and a minibar.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are about 22m² and sleep up to two people. They have a balcony with a lake view.</p>
<p><strong>Luxury Rooms </strong>are about 25m² and sleep up to three people. They have a terrace with a lake views, a king size bed, spa bath and separate shower. These rooms are only available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Classic Rooms for sole use </strong>are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
